# FREQ Fleet Registry
# Format: IP  LABEL  TYPE  [GROUPS]
# Types: linux, pve, truenas, pfsense, idrac, switch, docker
#
# Add hosts with: freq host add
# Discover hosts: freq host discover
#
# Example entries:
# 192.168.1.10  node1       pve       prod,cluster
# 192.168.1.11  node2       pve       prod,cluster
# 192.168.1.20  nas         truenas   prod,storage
# 192.168.1.1   firewall    pfsense   prod,network
# 192.168.1.50  app-server  docker    prod,apps
# 192.168.1.60  dev-box     linux     lab,dev
